---
title: Creamy Mushroom Spaghetti with Garlic Chips
description: Silky, smooth and packed with umami! That's what awaits with every bite of this creamy mushroom pasta. Fried garlic chips and basil are the perfect toppings for a hit of savoury crunch and sweet freshness!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spaghettis-cremeux-aux-champignons-0fd54944.jpg
